zenitysec/awesome-low-code","categoryHTML":"<h2>Other Lists</h2><h3>Power Platform (Microsoft)</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Power-Maverick/awesome-power-platform\">Awesome Microsoft Power Platform</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/Power-Maverick/awesome-power-platform\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">42</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":42,\"repo\":\"Power-Maverick/awesome-power-platform\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - A collection of awesome things regarding the Power Platform ecosystem.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-10-05T13:26:14.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"edm00se/awesome-board-games","categoryHTML":"<h2>Strategy</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgame/249381/estates\">The Estates</a></h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Players take on the role of investors seeking to make the most money by developing buildings in The Estates. The Estates is a new urban development featuring high-end infrastructure and a modern atmosphere for its citizens. The City Council recently approved the zoning map for The Estates. It calls for two rows of four buildings each, located between the River and Main Street. The meadows on the other side of the River are to remain a recreational area for the City. Players will bid for the various building pieces and place them in The Estates to their benefit. All buildings in completed rows score positive points, while all buildings in incomplete rows score negative points. It is possible to have zero completed rows of buildings. At the end, the player with the highest score wins The Estates!</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/AvC3AzHo8JlcvgKtQ3PDWA__itemrep/img/fKXzvy-mkwqrTORbPC-aNLB_ei8=/fit-in/246x300/filters:strip_icc()/pic4071903.jpg\" alt=\"The Estates image\"></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"right\">Players</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Min. Age</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Time</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"right\">2 - 5</td>\n<td align=\"right\">10</td>\n<td align=\"right\">40-60m</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"right\">### <a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgame/40182/telepathy\">Telepathy</a></td>\n<td align=\"right\"></td>\n<td align=\"right\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<blockquote>\n<p>In this puzzle solving challenge of deduction, logic and intuition, players go head to head to see who can be the first to guess their opponent's secret square. Every action turn brings you closer to finding the hidden, ancient symbol. But watch out; your opponent may be closer to solving your secret square than you think! The Telepathy board game is an outstanding logic building tool, ideal for educators and puzzle solvers alike. If you like Sudoku, Mastermind, or Battleship, this game is for you.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/HUrpAkrqZVwcjN8HXzaZaQ__itemrep/img/glE42FIgi4qCUEiDZxT_qJ1Vckk=/fit-in/246x300/filters:strip_icc()/pic5283740.jpg\" alt=\"Telepathy Image\"></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"right\">Players</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Min. Age</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Time</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"right\">2 - 4</td>\n<td align=\"right\">12</td>\n<td align=\"right\">20m</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","updatedAt":"2021-10-05T13:16:51.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"edm00se/awesome-board-games","categoryHTML":"<h2>Party</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgame/40692/small-world\">Small World</a></h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>An area control game where players control different fantasy races with a unique set of abilities. The goal is to conquer and control as much of the player board as possible and halting your opponents' expansion. When your race can't expand any further you let it fall into decline and pick a new race to continue the quest for dominance.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/aoPM07XzoceB-RydLh08zA__itemrep/img/vxZGxHhrtnOMxPM38WNIu-tfYmI=/fit-in/246x300/filters:strip_icc()/pic428828.jpg\" alt=\"Small World game image\"></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"right\">Players</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Min. Age</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Time</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"right\">2 - 5</td>\n<td align=\"right\">8</td>\n<td align=\"right\">40-80m</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","updatedAt":"2021-10-05T13:15:34.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ramnes/awesome-mongodb","categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Articles</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://blog.apify.com/tuning-mongodb-performance/\">Tuning MongoDB performance for production systems (Marek Trunkat, Apify)</a> - The techniques and MongoDB Cloud features to debug performance issues and expose sub-optimal queries</li>","updatedAt":"2021-10-05T13:14:48.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"vuejs/awesome-vue","categoryHTML":"<h2>Components &#x26; Libraries</h2><h4>Admin Template</h4>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Mani1124/vue-admin-template\">Vue-Admin-Template</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/Mani1124/vue-admin-template\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-r